Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.resources

Interface Summary
TemplateFinder Used by a parser to find a template by name.
TemplateStoreFinder Used by a serialiser to find a location to store a template.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTemplateFinder Abstract superclass that simplifies implementing the template finder interface.
AbstractTemplateStoreFinder Makes it easier to implement the template store finder interface.
ClassPathTemplateFinder Looks for templates in the class path.
FileSystemTemplateFinder Uses the file system to find templates.
FileSystemTemplateStoreFinder Finds locations for templates on the file system.
InMemoryTemplateStoreFinder A template store finder that finds in-memory output streams.
 

Exception Summary
ResourceException Thrown by template finders and template store finders when they can't create a stream.
